edu.jhu.en605681.HikeType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<HikeType>, Constable
public enum HikeType extends Enum<HikeType>
HikeType is an enum that provides identifiers and names for each of the hikes used in the BHC example for 605.681.
Author:
Robert Evans and Rich Spiegel
